{"tid":1752718,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<打完細boss打中boss>立法會競選籌備要開始展開","createTime":"2019-11-24T23:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T06:05:57.000Z","uid":137220,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea70ef6707d97d9047922a094a849d5ec19943c9","tid":1752718,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:13:32.000Z","msg":"雖然今次區選贏咗<br />\n<br />\n但立法會仍然不用樂觀，仍然有極大挑戰<br />\n因為立法會投票嘅玩法，比起區議會係hard mode，難玩好多<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">直選議席</span><br />\n建制派其實仲有四成鐵票, 喺<span style=\"color: red;\">比例代表制</span>之下，呢度已經夠佢哋拎好多議席<br />\n<br />\n而直選議席最難係<span style=\"color: red;\">配票</span>，係以往，建制派一路係玩得好過泛民/本土好多，因為佢哋有強大嘅組織同選舉機器<br />\n<br />\n雖然<span style=\"color: red;\">今時唔同往日</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">網絡動員</span>同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">團結</span>令到今次選舉 唔再完全favor建制<br />\n<br />\n但係實際點樣配票仍然係充滿困難<br />\n由<span style=\"color: red;\">競選名單同人數</span>開始，就已經要深思熟慮，加上如何有效利用網路/科技組織配票，呢方面就需要大家嘅智慧。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">功能組別</span><br />\n<br />\n啲仆街<span style=\"color: red;\">公司票團體票</span>，一路以嚟都係畀建制派壟斷，甚至毫無競爭，以前連入場競選都做唔到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過，呢個遊戲仲難玩，但更加必須要玩 </span></span><br />\n過往一直都打唔撚入功能組別<br />\n我夠膽講，以前贏唔到唔係單止係因為制度問題，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">而係因為我哋懶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根本就冇撚理由係咁</span><br />\n全香港各行各業，冇理由全撚部都建制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩好多有見識嘅巴打一早已經睇到呢個問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">例如飲食界</span>，已經有好多巴絲組織緊參選，相信今日<span style=\"color: red;\">黃店</span>成為風潮，飲食界係其中一個好有希望打破壟斷嘅界別之一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講功能組別每一個組別嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">入場門檻，同玩法都有所區別</span><br />\n<br />\n我建議每一個功能組別都分開<span style=\"color: red;\">支戰線</span><br />\n<br />\n每一個都<span style=\"color: red;\">參與</span><br />\n每一個都要<span style=\"color: red;\">研究</span><br />\n每一個都要<span style=\"color: red;\">贏</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c527274e388ef78b743eed41c0b97a933eb785","tid":1752718,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d88234e1af4cd45158f9c4da013898a31bd81a","tid":1752718,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbb52ee43075ed51956e097f87e0beba6c2d5bd","tid":1752718,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0368b0d53331d5f1ff7a99f5d459704205bd5c0","tid":1752718,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:18:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全面進攻功能組別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cd0d2785c25cb05a31d351719926ce1d0926d3","tid":1752718,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"係咪抗爭完咗㗎啦？<br />\n淨係搞選舉唔使抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788f5515e10a14dd34da8f2180577ba4ccf5e178","tid":1752718,"uid":137220,"like":2,"disli